        "heading_TQiQGK": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The Breton Shirt, Reworked",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_6pw4GQ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We took the idea of the classic marinière (also called Breton Shirt) and reworked it with a different intention: lighter, softer, and more fluid on the body. The stripes stay, but the proportions change — a looser cut, a slightly widened boat neck, and a fit that feels relaxed rather than strict. Knitted cotton yark gives the piece a refined texture and an ease that’s very different from the traditional sailor shirt. Familiar in spirit, redesigned in everything else.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
