        "text_r77cRY": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our Breton Shirts come from just outside Venice, from a place where certain things are still done with intent. We chose a small family workshop not for romance, but for the way they work: measured, exact, and uninterested in shortcuts. There’s no mythology, no folklore — just people who know their craft and let the results speak.<br/>The result is a piece shaped by people who take their time, work with intention, and pay attention to the details that define everything else.</p>"
          }
